-- Module 4: Text-to-Video Ad Generation
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="lesson-content"><h2>Text-to-Video Ad Generation</h2><h3>AI-Powered Video Creative at Scale</h3><p>Text-to-video AI tools are revolutionizing ad creative production. Generate professional video ads from simple text descriptions in minutes. This technology democratizes video advertising and enables rapid creative testing at unprecedented scale.</p><h3>What is Text-to-Video Generation?</h3><p>AI systems that create videos from text prompts. Describe desired video in natural language. AI generates visuals, animations, transitions. Add voiceover and music automatically. Professional-quality output without video production skills. Dramatically reduces time and cost. Enables rapid creative iteration.</p><h3>Available AI Video Tools</h3><p>Runway ML for advanced video generation. Synthesia for AI avatar videos. Pictory for text-to-video conversion. Lumen5 for social media videos. InVideo AI for marketing content. Descript for video editing with AI. Each tool has unique strengths. Choose based on needs and budget.</p><h3>Creating Videos with AI</h3><p>Write detailed text description. Specify style, mood, pacing. Select visual elements and themes. Choose voiceover style. Add music preferences. Generate initial version. Refine through iterations. Export in ad-optimized formats. Process takes minutes, not days.</p><h3>Prompt Engineering for Video</h3><p>Clear, specific descriptions work best. Include visual style preferences. Specify pacing and transitions. Describe key scenes and moments. Mention brand elements. Define target audience context. Better prompts yield better results. Iteration improves output quality.</p><h3>Customization and Branding</h3><p>Add logo and brand colors. Include product imagery. Customize fonts and styles. Incorporate brand voice. Maintain visual consistency. Align with brand guidelines. Personalization ensures brand recognition. Professional appearance builds trust.</p><h3>Video Formats for Facebook Ads</h3><p>Square (1:1) for Feed placement. Vertical (9:16) for Stories and Reels. Landscape (16:9) for in-stream video. Each format optimized for placement. Generate multiple versions efficiently. Test performance across formats. AI tools handle format conversion easily.</p><h3>Optimizing AI-Generated Videos</h3><p>Keep videos concise (15-30 seconds ideal). Hook viewers in first 3 seconds. Include captions for sound-off viewing. Strong call-to-action. Mobile-optimized visuals. Test multiple variations. Analyze performance data. Iterate based on results.</p><h3>Combining AI with Human Creativity</h3><p>AI handles production, humans provide strategy. Creative direction from marketers. AI executes technical production. Human review and refinement. Best results combine both. AI speeds process, humans ensure quality. Collaborative approach maximizes effectiveness.</p><h3>Cost and Time Savings</h3><p>Traditional video production: thousands of dollars, weeks of time. AI generation: dollars or free, minutes to hours. Enables more creative testing. Faster campaign launches. Lower barrier to video advertising. Democratizes professional video creation. ROI improvement through efficiency.</p><h3>Use Cases for AI Video Ads</h3><p>Product demonstrations and features. Customer testimonials (with AI avatars). Explainer videos for services. Social proof and reviews. Limited-time offers and promotions. Brand storytelling. Educational content. Retargeting messages. Versatile across objectives.</p><h3>Quality Considerations</h3><p>AI quality improving rapidly but not perfect. Review all generated content. Ensure brand alignment. Check for errors or oddities. Test with target audience. Compare to professional production. Balance speed with quality. Set appropriate expectations.</p><h3>Best Practices</h3><p>Start with clear objectives. Write detailed prompts. Generate multiple variations. Test different styles. Include strong CTAs. Optimize for mobile. Add captions. Monitor performance. Iterate continuously. Combine with traditional creative when needed.</p><h3>Integration with Facebook Ads</h3><p>Upload AI videos to Ads Manager. Use in dynamic creative testing. Create video carousels. Test across placements. Combine with static images. A/B test AI vs traditional. Measure comparative performance. Scale what works best.</p><h3>Common Mistakes</h3><p>Vague prompts yield poor results. Skipping human review. Ignoring brand guidelines. Over-relying on AI. Not testing variations. Poor mobile optimization. Missing captions. Weak calls-to-action. Learn from mistakes.</p><h3>Future of AI Video Creation</h3><p>Improving realism and quality. More customization options. Better brand integration. Real-time personalization. Interactive video capabilities. Seamless platform integration. Lower costs and barriers. Mainstream adoption accelerating. Stay current with developments.</p><h3>Measuring Success</h3><p>Track video completion rates. Monitor engagement metrics. Measure click-through rates. Analyze conversion performance. Compare to benchmarks. Calculate cost per result. Assess ROI. Data drives optimization. Continuous improvement cycle.</p><h3>Key Takeaways</h3><ul><li>AI text-to-video tools enable rapid, affordable video creation</li><li>Generate professional ads from text descriptions in minutes</li><li>Multiple AI tools available with different strengths</li><li>Clear, detailed prompts produce better results</li><li>Customize with branding and optimize for placements</li><li>Combines AI efficiency with human creative direction</li><li>Dramatic cost and time savings vs traditional production</li><li>Quality improving rapidly, test and iterate continuously</li></ul><p>Next lesson explores Predicting Churn with AI.</p></div>'
WHERE title = 'Text-to-Video Ad Generation' AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1 FROM modules m JOIN courses c ON m.course_id = c.id 
    WHERE m.id = lessons.module_id AND c.title LIKE '%Facebook%Ads%Mastery%'
);

-- Module 5: Predicting Churn with AI
UPDATE lessons SET content = '<div class="lesson-content"><h2>Predicting Churn with AI</h2><h3>Using Machine Learning to Retain Customers</h3><p>Customer churn prediction uses AI to identify users likely to stop purchasing or engaging. This proactive approach enables targeted retention campaigns before customers leave. Understanding churn prediction maximizes customer lifetime value and reduces acquisition costs.</p><h3>What is Customer Churn?</h3><p>When customers stop buying or engaging with brand. Lost revenue and relationship. Costs more to acquire new customers than retain existing. Churn rate measures percentage of customers lost. High churn indicates problems. Reducing churn improves profitability significantly. Prevention better than replacement.</p><h3>Why AI for Churn Prediction?</h3><p>Humans cannot process all behavioral signals. AI analyzes thousands of data points. Identifies subtle patterns indicating churn risk. Predicts before customer actually leaves. Enables proactive intervention. More accurate than manual analysis. Scales across entire customer base. Continuous learning improves predictions.</p><h3>Data Sources for Churn Prediction</h3><p>Purchase history and frequency. Website and app engagement. Email open and click rates. Customer service interactions. Product usage patterns. Social media engagement. Payment history. Demographic information. More data improves accuracy.</p><h3>Churn Risk Indicators</h3><p>Declining purchase frequency. Reduced engagement levels. Negative customer service interactions. Abandoned carts increasing. Email unsubscribes. App usage dropping. Payment failures. Competitor engagement. AI identifies combinations predicting churn.</p><h3>Building Churn Prediction Models</h3><p>Collect historical customer data. Label churned vs retained customers. Train machine learning model. Test prediction accuracy. Deploy for real-time scoring. Continuously update with new data. Improve model over time. Technical expertise or tools required.</p><h3>AI Tools for Churn Prediction</h3><p>Facebook Predictive Analytics features. Google Analytics 4 predictive metrics. Specialized platforms like Pecan AI. CRM systems with AI capabilities. Custom models with data science teams. Choose based on data volume and budget. Integration with existing systems important.</p><h3>Facebook Churn Prediction Features</h3><p>Predictive audiences in Ads Manager. Identify users likely to churn. Create custom audiences automatically. Target with retention campaigns. Lookalike audiences of retained customers. Automated optimization for retention. Leverage platform AI capabilities. Accessible without data science expertise.</p><h3>Creating Retention Campaigns</h3><p>Target high-churn-risk segments. Personalized messaging addressing concerns. Special offers and incentives. Re-engagement content. Remind of product value. Address pain points. Win-back strategies. Test different approaches. Measure retention impact.</p><h3>Retention Campaign Strategies</h3><p>Exclusive discounts for at-risk customers. Early access to new products. Personalized product recommendations. Educational content about product value. Customer appreciation messages. Loyalty program promotions. Survey to understand issues. Proactive customer service outreach.</p><h3>Measuring Retention Success</h3><p>Track churn rate changes. Monitor customer lifetime value. Measure campaign response rates. Calculate retention cost vs acquisition cost. Assess ROI of retention efforts. Compare to control groups. Continuous measurement enables optimization. Data-driven retention strategy.</p><h3>Segmentation for Retention</h3><p>High-value customers (priority retention). Recent customers (prevent early churn). Long-term customers (maintain loyalty). Seasonal customers (re-engage). Different segments need different approaches. Personalization improves effectiveness. Resource allocation based on value.</p><h3>Timing Retention Campaigns</h3><p>Intervene before actual churn. Optimal window varies by business. Too early wastes resources. Too late loses customer. AI helps identify perfect timing. Test different intervention points. Refine based on results. Timing critical for success.</p><h3>Combining Churn Prediction with Facebook Ads</h3><p>Upload churn risk scores to custom audiences. Create lookalike audiences of loyal customers. Exclude churned customers from acquisition campaigns. Retarget at-risk customers with retention messages. Optimize ad delivery for retention. Measure impact on customer lifetime value. Integrated approach maximizes effectiveness.</p><h3>Best Practices</h3><p>Collect comprehensive customer data. Update predictions regularly. Act on predictions promptly. Personalize retention efforts. Test different strategies. Measure results rigorously. Iterate continuously. Combine AI with human insight. Proactive beats reactive.</p><h3>Common Challenges</h3><p>Insufficient data for accurate predictions. Data quality issues. Privacy and compliance concerns. Integration complexity. Acting on predictions at scale. Measuring true impact. Balancing automation and personalization. Resource constraints. Plan for challenges.</p><h3>Future of Churn Prediction</h3><p>More sophisticated AI models. Real-time prediction and intervention. Better integration across platforms. Automated retention campaigns. Predictive customer lifetime value. Enhanced personalization. Lower technical barriers. Mainstream adoption growing. Competitive necessity emerging.</p><h3>Key Takeaways</h3><ul><li>Churn prediction uses AI to identify at-risk customers proactively</li><li>Analyzes behavioral data to predict future churn likelihood</li><li>Enables targeted retention campaigns before customers leave</li><li>Facebook offers built-in predictive audience features</li><li>Retention cheaper than acquisition, improves profitability</li><li>Personalized campaigns based on churn risk most effective</li><li>Timing and segmentation critical for success</li><li>Continuous measurement and iteration essential</li></ul><p>Next module covers Scaling and Optimization strategies.</p></div>'
WHERE title = 'Predicting Churn with AI' AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1 FROM modules m JOIN courses c ON m.course_id = c.id 
    WHERE m.id = lessons.module_id AND c.title LIKE '%Facebook%Ads%Mastery%'
);
